Text: I don't know who you are, but I love you. I started watching this show when I was in England last year and haven't been able to find a way to watch it in the states. You are a life saver. THANK YOU SO MUCH for doing this and please keep it up. You don't know what it means to me !!!
A big thank you from Australia, have a great week!
thanks so much for the uploads, my mom loves this show and our pvr stopped working! your a life saver.
